Authentication
To access certain endpoints, authentication is required. Obtain a token by making a POST request to /api/auth/login with valid credentials.

Admin Access
Use the admin token to access admin-exclusive functionalities. Include the token in the request headers with the key Authorization.

Product Management
Add Product: POST request to /api/products
Get All Products: GET request to /api/products
Get Product by ID: GET request to /api/products/:id
Update Product: PUT request to /api/products/:id
Delete Product: DELETE request to /api/products/:id
Image Upload
Upload Image: POST request to /api/upload
Cart Validation
Validate Cart: POST request to /api/cart/validate
